    "member_count": 8,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "荇菜形态似微型睡 莲，花虽小，但密集 成片，有着不同情调 的景观效果。在长江 流域及以南地区的冬 季，荇菜还常以常绿 或半常绿形式生长; 在炎热的夏季长势缓 慢，在浅水水域甚至 出现枯黄现象。",
        "bbox": [
          0.7543597409068261,
          0.46563039723661487,
          0.9227703039362232,
          0.6376511226252158
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_1",
        "observed_type": "image_caption",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "在湿地公园中大面积应用的菜",
        "bbox": [
          0.06776283009466866,
          0.48497409326424873,
          0.2750373692077728,
          0.4987910189982729
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_2",
        "observed_type": "image_body",
        "canon_role": "picture",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
          0.0687593423019432,
          0.5126079447322971,
          0.7095166915794718,
          0.7875647668393783
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "纯菜属于一种高贵、 优良的水生蔬菜，但 产出比不高。在工程 应用上，可结合其经 济功能综合考虑配置。",
        "bbox": [
          0.7553562531141006,
          0.6556131260794473,
          0.9227703039362232,
          0.7412780656303972
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_3",
        "observed_type": "image_caption",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "盛花期的荇菜",
        "bbox": [
          0.06776283009466866,
          0.7930915371329879,
          0.15844544095665172,
          0.8069084628670121
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_8",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "品种、类似种",
        "bbox": [
          0.08071748878923767,
          0.8414507772020725,
          0.17239661185849528,
          0.8559585492227979
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "荇菜属有数个原品种，外形差异不。有景观效果类似的同属植物银莲 花（N.indica）、水莲（N.cristatum）等，花为白色，叶形与荇菜差异不大。 有景观效果近似的不同科属品种—莼菜（Braseniaschreberi），叶为椭圆形， 与荇菜叶形有区别，花较，红褐。",
        "bbox": [
          0.06576980568011959,
          0.8642487046632125,
          0.6915794718485302,
          0.9333333333333333
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "荇菜叶翠绿，小黄花密集， 精巧别致，是优良的小型浮叶 景观植物。",
        "bbox": [
          0.71350274040857,
          0.8649395509499136,
          0.9397110114598903,
          0.9146804835924007
        ],
        "order": 12
      }
    ]
